## Block Format

```json
{"opcode":"motion_movesteps","inputs":{"STEPS":[1,[4,"10"]]},"fields":{},"shadow":false,"topLevel":true}
```

Input: `[1,[4,"10"]]`=number, `[1,[10,"text"]]`=string, `[2,"blockId"]`=nested.

## Coordinate System
480×360 stage. x:[-240,240], y:[-180,180]. Direction: 0°=up, 90°=right.

## Python Scripts (zero deps)
- `scratch_utils.py`: pack, unpack, validate, create empty project, add sprites
- `block_builder.py`: 60+ convenience functions, ScriptBuilder, reporters
- `project_builder.py`: ScratchProject class (high-level API)

## Important Rules
- Every sprite ≥ 1 costume, Stage ≥ 1 backdrop
- Extensions go in `project.json` `extensions` list
- Validate with `validate_project()` before delivering
- Python 3.7+, no pip install needed
